#~ "<option>--prefix</option>=$<envar>KDEDIR</envar> where $<envar>KDEDIR</"
#~ "envar> is where the rest of &kde; is installed. This could vary widely, "
#~ "depending on the distribution and operating system you have. Better "
#~ "install &khangman; from your distribution!"
